886e2ff78d8a9083d71421fed8fdc8eea308da75bffb0f2eb6edd09c6606fc2a6706b0354a0f18191f3090e381d8885ea9961360c5cdcd959c4974959a176741  Fixup-some-warnings-about-using-NULL-where-it-shoudnt-be.patch"
